================================
=== OCS METS XML Export Plugin
=== Version: 1.0
=== Release date: 30/11/2007 
=== Authors: Scott Yeadon, Leo Monus
================================

About
-----
This plugin for OCS 2 provides an XML export feature using The Australian METS Journal Profile 1.0
for more information about the Schema go to the Library of Congress website
http://www.loc.gov/standards/mets/mets-registered-profiles.html

License
-------
This plugin is licensed under the GNU General Public License v2. See the file COPYING for the complete terms of this license.

System Requirements
-------------------
Same requirements as the OCS 2.0.x core.

Installation
------------
To install the plugin:
- copy the mets folder into OCS/plugins/importexport

The export functionality can then be accessed through:
- Home > User > Conference Manager > Import/Export Data > METS XML Export Plugin

